Proto-PROPOSAL DB12 (Vanyel)
Loans
(Creates a Rule)

If a Player believes that e is in need of extra Marks, he may request a
Loan from the Banker.  The granting of such a loan is at the Banker's
discretion.  Any money received from such a loan must be paid to the
Bank, plus .1 Mark for each day since the loan was first granted.  A loan
is not considered to be paid off until all marks have been paid back,
and all additional .1Mk have been paid.

***END PROTO

Revision history:
first proto 27 Sep 1994 3:45 AM CDT

Well, wha do you think?  It's kinda rough around the edges now, but we
could prolly work it out fairly well.

Vanyel

